        "TileImage": "$($repository 207f8711-832d-4458-89ea-ae6a9c5761af).Image",
        "Description": "PatrikkiBobi felt himself growing lighter, his colors softening like distant echoes. As he drifted near the reef, Squidward noticed something was wrong. He approached quietly, watching PatrikkiBobi shimmer and blur.\r\r“You were always louder than the ocean,” Squidward said softly.\r\rPatrikkiBobi smiled faintly. As the currents passed through him, he slowly faded away. Squidward stood alone afterward, realizing that even things that seem endless can disappear—and be missed more than expected.",
